      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有狐.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有狐綏綏，在彼淇梁，心之憂矣，之子無裳。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is a fox, solitary and suspicious,
At that deep ford of the K'e.
My heart is sad; —
That man has no lower garment.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
